name: Alienware Gaming Headset Case – AW988, AW310H, AW510H | Dell USA
description: Protect your important Headset with Alienware Gaming Headset Case. With all the gear a gamer must carry, the Alienware Gaming Headset Case is essential for protecting one of your most valuable assets - your headset. Designed to keep your headphones safe while keeping everything organized, the Alienware Gaming Headset Case is constructed from durable, water-resistant nylon. It is padded for extra protection while boasting Velcro straps to secure your headset in place, while internal mesh pockets secure and store your related gear.
